      • Public Sub PopulateMigrationActivityListBox()

        Public Sub PopulateMigrationActivityListBox()
        Details:

        '* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
        '* Sub/Fn : PopulateMigrationTaskWindow
        '* Description : Populate Migration Task window with + nodes at Zero level
        '* Created : 09-11-2015 01:19
        '* Modified: 09-11-2015 01:19
        '* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
        'Public Sub PopulateMigrationTaskWindow()
        ' On Error GoTo Err_PopulateMigrationTaskWindow
        '
        ' Dim colActivities As Collection
        ' Set colActivities = New Collection
        '
        ' InitializeMigrationTaskPadRanges
        '
        ' On Error Resume Next
        '
        ' Dim lngRow As Long
        '
        ' For lngRow = 2 To rngMigrationActivities.Rows.count
        ' 'colActivities.Add rngMigrationActivities.Cells(lngRow, MIGRATION_ACTIVITY_COLUMNS.ACTIVITY__).Value & PIPE_CHAR & rngMigrationActivities.Cells(lngRow, MIGRATION_ACTIVITY_COLUMNS.SUB_ACTIVITY__).Value
        ' colActivities.Add rngMigrationActivities.Cells(lngRow, MIGRATION_ACTIVITY_COLUMNS.SUB_ACTIVITY__).Value
        ' Next lngRow
        '
        ' lstMigrationActivity.Clear
        ' lstMigrationActivity.ColumnCount = 7
        '
        ' lstMigrationActivity.ColumnWidths = "400,0,0,0,0,0,0"
        '
        ' Dim lngCount As Long
        '
        ' Dim nodeStr As String
        ' Dim lastNode As String
        ' Dim lstRow As Long: lstRow = 0
        ' For lngCount = 1 To colActivities.count
        ' lastNode = colActivities.item(lngCount)
        ' nodeStr = GetTreeBasedHierarchyString(colActivities.item(lngCount), lastNode, 4)
        ' lstMigrationActivity.AddItem
        ' lstMigrationActivity.List(lstRow, 0) = nodeStr
        ' lstRow = lstRow + 1
        ' Next lngCount
        '
        '
        '' Adding + 1st node into Tree
        '' Dim lngCount As Long
        '' For lngCount = 1 To colActivities.count
        '' lstMigrationActivity.AddItem Space(1 * TAB_LENGTH) & "+ " & colActivities.item(lngCount)
        '' lstMigrationActivity.List(lstMigrationActivity.ListCount - 1, 1) = colActivities.item(lngCount)
        '' lstMigrationActivity.List(lstMigrationActivity.ListCount - 1, 2) = "1"
        '' Next lngCount
        '
        ' Me.Show 1
        '
        ' Exit Sub
        'Err_PopulateMigrationTaskWindow:
        ' MsgBox Err.Description, vbOKOnly + vbCritical, "Error occured in PopulateMigrationTaskWindow"
        'End Sub
        '* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
        '* Sub/Fn : PopulateMigrationActivityListBox
        '* Description : Populate Migration Activity ListBox
        '* Created : 09-11-2015 02:01
        '* Modified: 09-11-2015 02:01
        '* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
